00:36:51,250 --> 00:36:53,708
Seperti Ibu yang tak punya pilihan
selain disiksa

495
00:36:54,708 --> 00:36:55,583
oleh Tian Ching.

496
00:36:58,625 --> 00:36:59,583
Itu semua salah Ibu.

497
00:37:00,208 --> 00:37:02,250
Ibu tak mengajarinya dengan baik.

498
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:05,416
Ibu.

499
00:37:06,875 --> 00:37:09,458
Aku tak mau melihat Ibu menderita lagi.

500
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:13,000
Bisa izinkan aku membantu Ibu?

501
00:37:30,333 --> 00:37:32,291
Apa pun yang terjadi kepada Li Lan...

502
00:37:35,125 --> 00:37:36,500
itu bukan salahmu.

503
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:21,916
Pak Wong, mau bermain di pinggir danau?

504
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:24,750
Pak Wong, tangkap aku!

505
00:38:25,166 --> 00:38:26,791
Pak Wong, jangan lari!

506
00:38:34,166 --> 00:38:35,916
Kau sudah tua.

507
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:37,458
Benar.

508
00:38:38,416 --> 00:38:39,625
Dan kau masih anak-anak.

509
00:38:43,166 --> 00:38:44,500
Maafkan aku.

510
00:38:45,083 --> 00:38:46,333
Pada saat itu,

511
00:38:47,500 --> 00:38:48,916
aku tak bisa menyelamatkanmu.

512
00:38:52,833 --> 00:38:53,666
Tak apa.

513
00:38:54,416 --> 00:38:56,291
Jika kau suka,

514
00:38:56,958 --> 00:38:59,083
kita bisa berenang bersama.

515
00:39:02,333 --> 00:39:03,291
Baik.

516
00:39:40,750 --> 00:39:41,958
Sudah temukan orang itu?

517
00:39:42,041 --> 00:39:43,416
Aku belum pastikan.

518
00:39:45,708 --> 00:39:47,000
Dia tadi menciummu.

519
00:39:49,750 --> 00:39:50,916
Kau membiarkannya?

520
00:39:52,250 --> 00:39:53,375
Aku punya pilihan?

521
00:39:54,625 --> 00:39:55,500
Begitu.

522
00:40:04,875 --> 00:40:06,500
Hei, lihat.

523
00:40:06,583 --> 00:40:07,500
Sepatu hijau.

524
00:40:11,625 --> 00:40:13,333
Diakah yang kita cari?

525
00:40:15,125 --> 00:40:16,458
Aku akan mengawasinya.

526
00:40:16,791 --> 00:40:19,083
Jika benar, dia akan terpancing.

527
00:40:19,916 --> 00:40:22,541
Baik, aku akan kembali ke Tian Ching.

528
00:40:22,625 --> 00:40:23,708
Hati-hati.

529
00:41:00,875 --> 00:41:01,916
Hei.

530
00:41:05,375 --> 00:41:07,000
Aku bawa yang kau mau.

531
00:41:09,791 --> 00:41:12,791
Jadi, kau hakim yang disogok Tian Ching.

532
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:16,250
Jangan macam-macam.

533
00:41:16,875 --> 00:41:18,416
Bisa beri tahu aku

534
00:41:19,333 --> 00:41:20,583
berapa nomor hakimmu?

535
00:41:22,375 --> 00:41:23,541
Nomor enam.

536
00:41:28,208 --> 00:41:30,083
Penjaga Surga?

537
00:41:34,083 --> 00:41:35,333
Hakim perempuan?

538
00:41:36,416 --> 00:41:38,166
Aku tak tahu ada hakim perempuan.

539
00:41:38,625 --> 00:41:40,416
Itulah pendapat orang.

540
00:41:41,625 --> 00:41:43,375
Kau bisa bertahan di Alam Baka

541
00:41:43,458 --> 00:41:45,416
cukup lama tanpa kekuatan.

542
00:41:46,083 --> 00:41:47,416
Kau sungguh hebat.

543
00:41:50,125 --> 00:41:52,000
Kau hancurkan keseimbangan alam semesta

544
00:41:52,083 --> 00:41:54,166
demi mutiara konyol ini?

545
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:56,750
Aku datang untuk menangkap...

546
00:42:02,041 --> 00:42:03,750
Sudah beberapa ribu tahun.

547
00:42:04,458 --> 00:42:05,791
Siapa bisa hentikan aku?

548
00:42:14,916 --> 00:42:15,833
Ibu...

549
00:42:17,250 --> 00:42:19,541
Ibu ingin berhenti tunduk
kepada Tian Ching?

550
00:42:22,041 --> 00:42:24,000
Ibu tak takut dia akan marah?

551
00:42:26,083 --> 00:42:27,625
Ini demi kebaikannya.

552
00:42:31,833 --> 00:42:33,250
Baru saja,

553
00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:36,125
ada yang bilang mau membantu Ibu.

554
00:42:39,583 --> 00:42:40,458
Benar.

555
00:42:41,166 --> 00:42:44,250
Tampaknya dia orang yang hebat.

556
00:42:46,333 --> 00:42:48,125
Lagi pula, dia putri Ibu.

557
00:43:00,833 --> 00:43:02,833
Wong, kami menemukan pembunuhnya!

558
00:43:02,916 --> 00:43:05,458
Fu Mei, salah satu pelayan Lim.

559
00:43:06,041 --> 00:43:06,916
Wong?

560
00:43:09,583 --> 00:43:10,416
Wong?

561
00:43:13,166 --> 00:43:14,083
Wong?

562
00:43:16,416 --> 00:43:17,625
Wong?

563
00:43:34,000 --> 00:43:35,291
Wong...

564
00:43:39,250 --> 00:43:40,750
Wong...

565
00:43:43,541 --> 00:43:45,000
Istirahatlah dengan tenang.

566
00:43:50,708 --> 00:43:51,833
Wong...

567
00:44:03,791 --> 00:44:04,791
Sayang.

568
00:44:06,750 --> 00:44:07,750
Ikut denganku.

569
00:44:09,583 --> 00:44:10,708
Kita mau ke mana?

570
00:44:15,833 --> 00:44:18,583
Kau mengundang tamu yang berkualitas.

571
00:44:18,833 --> 00:44:20,250
Dialah yang mencuri

572
00:44:20,333 --> 00:44:21,833
Mutiara Hitam.

573
00:44:22,291 --> 00:44:24,125
Dia Penjaga Surga.

574
00:44:27,541 --> 00:44:28,875
Kau kenal dia?

575
00:44:34,458 --> 00:44:36,041
- Tidak.
- Begitu?

576
00:44:37,125 --> 00:44:39,541
Dia memperhatikanmu di jamuan,

577
00:44:39,625 --> 00:44:41,250
serasa teman lamamu.

578
00:44:43,375 --> 00:44:44,375
Begitukah?

579
00:44:45,458 --> 00:44:46,375
Hei.

580
00:44:47,041 --> 00:44:48,875
Aku dengar banyak soal dirimu.

581
00:44:49,833 --> 00:44:51,375
Akhirnya, bisa menemuimu.

582
00:44:51,833 --> 00:44:55,583
Setelah melihatmu, aku akhirnya paham
kenapa orang membencimu.

583
00:44:56,375 --> 00:44:57,958
Itu karena kau begitu hina.

584
00:45:01,791 --> 00:45:04,125
Sayang, kembalilah ke jamuan.

585
00:45:05,666 --> 00:45:09,166
Aku mau menyambut langsung
tamu dari Surga ini.

586
00:45:14,791 --> 00:45:15,750
Sayang.

587
00:45:19,958 --> 00:45:22,333
Jadi, aku hina, ya?

588
00:45:22,416 --> 00:45:24,041
Kau pikir sedang di mana?

589
00:45:36,083 --> 00:45:37,875
Selamat datang di Neraka.

590
00:45:42,375 --> 00:45:44,166
- Ibu.
- Tian Ching melukaimu?

591
00:45:44,250 --> 00:45:46,416
Tidak, tetapi Er Lang butuh bantuan kita.

592
00:45:46,500 --> 00:45:47,333
Baik.

593
00:45:49,458 --> 00:45:50,333
Ayo.

594
00:46:00,791 --> 00:46:02,041
Tian Ching sudah pergi.

595
00:46:04,083 --> 00:46:04,916
Ayo bergerak!

596
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:07,041
Ibu, tetap di sini.

597
00:46:07,125 --> 00:46:08,625
Aku tak mau Ibu kena masalah.

598
00:46:08,708 --> 00:46:10,541
Lebih baik jika kita lakukan bersama.

599
00:46:10,750 --> 00:46:12,416
Aku tahu cara menghadapi Tian Ching.

600
00:46:13,291 --> 00:46:14,708
Namun, jika dia melihat Ibu...

601
00:46:16,916 --> 00:46:19,041
Baik, hati-hatilah.

602
00:46:23,583 --> 00:46:24,583
Er Lang.

603
00:46:25,875 --> 00:46:28,041
Er Lang, bangun.

604
00:46:28,666 --> 00:46:29,666
Cepat bangun.

605
00:46:30,125 --> 00:46:31,708
Li Lan? Kenapa kau kembali?

606
00:46:31,791 --> 00:46:34,041
Tak ada waktu lagi. Kita harus pergi.

607
00:46:34,750 --> 00:46:36,166
Ke mana para penjaganya?

608
00:46:38,375 --> 00:46:39,666
Dia membiarkanmu masuk?

609
00:46:40,916 --> 00:46:42,666
Dia pergi, jadi aku menyelinap.

610
00:46:46,125 --> 00:46:47,708
Untuk apa dia pergi?

611
00:46:47,791 --> 00:46:49,000
Mana kutahu?

612
00:46:49,208 --> 00:46:50,208
Ini tak benar.

613
00:46:52,208 --> 00:46:53,166
Tempurung kura-kura.

614
00:46:53,375 --> 00:46:55,416
Li Lan, aku harus merebut tempurungku.

615
00:46:55,666 --> 00:46:56,666
Tempurung apa?

616
00:46:56,750 --> 00:46:57,916
Tian Ching mengambilnya.

617
00:46:58,083 --> 00:47:00,458
Itu sangat penting. Harus kurebut kembali.

618
00:47:01,750 --> 00:47:02,916
Mari kita cari bersama.

619
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:04,166
- Ayo.
- Tak bisa gerak.

620
00:47:04,458 --> 00:47:05,333
Bersandar kepadaku.

621
00:47:13,291 --> 00:47:14,375
Li Lan-ku sayang.

622
00:47:15,625 --> 00:47:17,291
Andai saja aku salah.

623
00:47:20,750 --> 00:47:22,333
Kenapa mengkhianatiku

624
00:47:23,291 --> 00:47:25,125
dan bekerja sama dengannya?

625
00:47:35,333 --> 00:47:37,458
Aku sudah tak sabar
menanti pernikahan kita.

626
00:47:41,250 --> 00:47:44,125
Lebih baik mati daripada menikahimu.

627
00:47:46,666 --> 00:47:48,041
Pan Li Lan.

628
00:47:50,333 --> 00:47:52,166
Aku kecewa kepadamu!

629
00:48:07,375 --> 00:48:09,500
Kini makin menyenangkan.

630
00:48:19,958 --> 00:48:21,166
Hentikan!

